<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Noel hmasa bik a chuahnak cu, Vanmi nih tlimno rawn i tuukhal an chimh
 hna, Tlimno rawn i tuu an zoh lioah, Cu khuasik khuamawt le zantim ah cun.

[C1]
   Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel, Israel Siangpahrang a chuak.

[V2]
 Van an zoh, arfi pakhat an hmuh: Nichuah nak lei lam hlapi ah khin a
 ceu i, Vawlei cung ah fak piin a ceu, Chun le zan hlan in a ceu cam cin
 ko.

[C2]
   Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel, Israel Siangpahrang a chuak.

[V3]
 Cu arfi ceunak zoh in mifim, Pathum nichuahnak lei lamhlapi in an ra,
 Siangpahrang pakhat kawl an tum i, Arfi kha khuazeika hmanh ah an zulh.

[C3]
   Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel, Israel Siangpahrang a chuak.

[V4]
 Nitlaklei ah hi arfi aa thawn, Bethlehem khua cungah mi chimh bang aa
 din ko, Khika khin a tang i a um colh; Bawi Jesuh Khrih ihnak cung zawn
 te ah.

[C4]
   Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel, Israel Siangpahrang a chuak.

[V5]
 Mifim pathum hna cu an vung lut, Hmaizahnak le upatnak in an khuk an
 bil, An laksawng sung bik kha i put in, An sui le marh le frankinsens an
 pek.

[C5]
   Noel, Noel, Noel, Noel, Israel Siangpahrang a chuak.</lyrics>
